{"tid":539412,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"22:20【臥虎2 / 追龍 2017】富貴險中求","createTime":"2018-01-24T13:50:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-24T16:01:30.000Z","uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9210ce574942a7c8fb8c00cefeb7fb3dce09e687","tid":539412,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T13:50:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsites.simbla.com%2F871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a%2Fiusee&d=d7HHhTYFsV4hwRhSgS4PEfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=b3b11b29\" target=\"_blank\">http://sites.simbla.com/871f3a54-3131-b616-e5df-b781f31a0a3a/iusee</a><br />\n<br />\n　　電影講述了香港現代史上兩大著名狠角色大毒梟跛豪（甄子丹飾）、五億探長雷洛（劉德華飾）的傳奇故事。 <br />\n　　上世紀六七十年代，香港由英國殖民，權勢腐敗、社會混亂。1963年，窮困潦倒的青年阿豪（甄子丹飾）偷渡至香港，抱著&ldquo;生死有命、富貴在天&rdquo;之心決意一搏人生。阿豪帶著幾個兄弟，從九龍城寨底層開始一路刀刃舔血，爬上香港毒品霸主之位，一手掌控香港十大黑幫，江湖人稱&ldquo;跛豪&rdquo;。而雷洛（劉德華飾）則從一位普通探長一步步爬上華人總探長高位，統領全香港三萬警察，手握香港治安&ldquo;潛規則&rdquo;。為壟斷香港黃賭毒三大經濟產業，跛豪與雷洛結拜為兄弟，兩人一黑一白兩手遮天，權勢滔天，家財億萬，獨霸香港島&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com/t51.2885-15/e35/23733889_1483657585048660_4121561478937444352_n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sea1-1.cdninstagram.com%2Ft51.2885-15%2Fe35%2F23733889_1483657585048660_4121561478937444352_n.jpg&h=855cda98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3de5bfbbd89d377943b08880cf78f43ed62e6fcc","tid":539412,"uid":34643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-24T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}